sql:
SELECT notification_id, notification_date
FROM notifications
ORDER BY notification_date DESC;

external_knowledge:
- Alerts in this context refer to notifications;
- Each notification is counted towards the role of the user who received it;
- Roles represent different user types in the system, such as Admin, Faculty, or Student.

- In this metaphorical scenario, "stars" represent users who are actively participating in "educational events" or "academic engagements".;
- "Shining the brightest" metaphorically refers to having the highest attendance count.;
- The latest attendance status is a reflection of the user's most recent participation activity.;
